    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your skill with lighter weapons allows you to wield one alongside your net.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Dex 15, Exotic Weapon Proficiency (net), Net Adept, Two-Weapon Fighting.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You can treat a net as a one-handed ranged weapon, allowing you to wield a light or one-handed melee weapon and still make ranged attacks with your net. When you use your light or one-handed melee weapon to attack an entangled opponent, you gain a +2 bonus on damage rolls and on attack rolls to confirm a critical hit.<br/><br/><b>Normal</b><br/>A net is a two-handed ranged weapon.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you use a light or one-handed melee weapon to attack an opponent entangled by your net, you can spend up to 5 stamina points when you hit the opponent to gain a bonus on the damage roll equal to double the number of stamina points you spent.",
